data.text:
Former Fulton County prosecutor looks head to Trump election meddling trial ATLANTA (WUPA) - A former Fulton County prosecutor familiar with the players in the Trump indictment case shares what we can expect as we look ahead toward the trial. Clint Rucker, a local attorney and judge in the cities of East Point and South Fulton, retired from the Fulton County District Attorney's Office after 25 years.
